01:02:45.907 --> 01:02:51.449
and the information on that is
in your reading.

01:02:51.449 --> 01:02:55.675
Here is the story on--with this
drop in marriage,

01:02:55.675 --> 01:02:59.989
and this is all women,
it's not just teenagers.

01:02:59.989 --> 01:03:04.250
Look at the rise in unmarried
births.

01:03:04.250 --> 01:03:09.273
It's about a third of all
