01:11:45.618 --> 01:11:48.703
We're coming to the end,
we are at the end,

01:11:48.703 --> 01:11:50.979
and there's lots more to say.
 

01:11:50.979 --> 01:11:53.270
Let me tell you one more thing.
 

01:11:53.270 --> 01:11:55.670
The whole pattern of
